OL,3,CPupil told self, 'What am I doing,
OL,4,Cstop' during school stabbing
OL,6,FA teenage girl, who stabbed teachers
OL,7,Fand a pupil during a school attack in
OL,8,FApril, thought "what am I doing, stop"
OL,9,Fas she launched her attack, a court
OL,10,Fhas heard.
OL,12,FTeachers Fiona Elias, Elizabeth Hopkin
OL,13,Fand a female pupil required hospital
OL,14,Ftreatment after the stabbing at Ysgol
OL,15,FDyffryn Aman which sent the school
OL,16,Finto lockdown.
OL,18,FThe 14 year-old defendant who can't be
OL,19,Fnamed gave evidence today at Swansea
OL,20,FCrown Court.
