OL,3,CPupil told self, 'What am I doing,
OL,4,Cstop' during school stabbing
OL,6,FShe denies three counts of attempted
OL,7,Fmurder after previously pleading
OL,8,Fguilty to three counts of wounding
OL,9,Fwith intent and one of possession of a
OL,10,Fbladed article on school premises.
OL,12,FThe defendant, wearing a black
OL,13,Fjumpsuit and tie, took to the witness
OL,14,Fstand and told a jury she wished she
OL,15,Fcould take back what she had done.
OL,17,FShe said: "It doesn't feel like I did
OL,18,Fit, to be honest. (I feel) terrible,
OL,19,Fguilty."
