OL,3,CPupil told self, 'What am I doing,
OL,4,Cstop' during school stabbing
OL,6,FThe girl said she did not intend to
OL,7,Fkill any of the people who were
OL,8,Finjured, and that she could not
OL,9,Fremember large parts of the incident.
OL,11,FAsk to describe what she remembered
OL,12,Fshe added: "You can't, it's dark, to
OL,13,Fsay the least, I remember being very
OL,14,Fhot during the incident."
OL,16,FThe defendant told the jury leading up
OL,17,Fto the stabbing she had no intention
OL,18,Fof hurting Ms Elias despite joking
OL,19,Fwith friends about "slapping or
OL,20,Fpunching" her.
