OL,3,CPupil told self, 'What am I doing,
OL,4,Cstop' during school stabbing
OL,6,FAsked what she intended to do as she
OL,7,Fapproached Ms Elias the defendant said
OL,8,Fshe was going to "hit Ms Elias with
OL,9,Fher hands".
OL,11,FIn response to being questioned why
OL,12,Fshe struck Ms Elias with the knife the
OL,13,Fdefendant said "I'm unaware, I dont
OL,14,Fremember I'm afraid."
OL,16,FThe defendant replied "no" when asked
OL,17,Fif she intended to murder any of the
OL,18,Fvictims in this case.
