OL,3,CPupil told self, 'What am I doing,
OL,4,Cstop' during school stabbing
OL,6,FThe defendant told the court she hid
OL,7,Fthe multi-tool knife in her pockets
OL,8,Fand under her bed to avoid detection
OL,9,Fby her father.
OL,11,FFriends of the defendant told the
OL,12,Fcourt how she had shown them the knife
OL,13,Fon the morning of the attack and told
OL,14,Fthem she "was going to do something
OL,15,Fstupid".
