OL,6,FCCTV played to the court showed the
OL,7,Fthen 13-year-old stabbing the floor of
OL,8,Fthe school hall with the multi-tool
OL,9,Fknife.
OL,11,FIn it, the defendant can be seen
OL,12,Finteracting with Ms Elias, before
OL,13,Flunging at her with the knife.
OL,15,FIn evidence played to the jury, both
OL,16,Fteachers told how they thought "they
OL,17,Fwould die" during the attack.
