OL,6,FThe defendant had moved to Ysgol
OL,7,FDyffryn Aman from another school after
OL,8,Fbeing the victim of bullying her
OL,9,Ffather previously told the court.
OL,11,FHe said she had been verbally and
OL,12,Fphysically attacked, with eggs thrown
OL,13,Fat the family home.
OL,15,FThe trial, which has entered its fifth
OL,16,Fday, continues.
